	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" >Alexandre Soljenitsyne</h1>


	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
			<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">Un article de Wikipédia, l&#039;encyclopédie libre.</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirigé depuis <a href="/w/index.php?title=Aleksandr_Solzhenitsyn&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Aleksandr Solzhenitsyn">Aleksandr Solzhenitsyn</a>)</span></div>
		<div id="contentSub2"></div>
		
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="fr" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="infobox_v3">
