<div>Alexandre Soljenitsyne</div>
</div><div class="images"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow,_December_1998.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Description de cette image, également commentée ci-après" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a1/Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow%2C_December_1998.jpg/220px-Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow%2C_December_1998.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="230" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a1/Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow%2C_December_1998.jpg/330px-Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow%2C_December_1998.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a1/Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow%2C_December_1998.jpg/440px-Alexander_Solzhenitsyn_in_Moscow%2C_December_1998.jpg 2x" data-file-width="481" data-file-height="503" /></a> 
