<h3><span id="Po.C3.A9sie"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Poésie">Poésie</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Alexandre_Soljenitsyne&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=20" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Poésie">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Alexandre_Soljenitsyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Modifier la section : Poésie">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><i>Le Chemin des forçats</i> (<a href="/wiki/2014" title="2014">2014</a>)</li></ul>
<h3><span id="Essais_et_M.C3.A9moires"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Essais_et_Mémoires">Essais et Mémoires</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Alexandre_Soljenitsyne&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=21" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Essais et Mémoires">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Alexandre_Soljenitsyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Modifier la section : Essais et Mémoires">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><i>Les Droits de l'écrivain</i> (<a href="/wiki/1969" title="1969">1969</a>)</li>
